BACnet,is,a,data,communication,protocol,for,building,automation,and,control,networks,It,was,designed,to,allow,such,networks,to,communicate,with,heating,ventilation,air,conditioning,lighting,access,and,fire,detection,systems,and,their,associated,equipment,BACnet,Help,assists,users,in,making,full,use,of,their,BACnet,networks,by,letting,them,take,snapshots,of,networks,for,immediate,or,future,reference,BACnet,Help,s,functions,are,accessible,using,REST,calls,in,JSON,format